<% @page_title = "Oops!" %>

<div class="padding">
  <p>We're sorry, but the page you requested is not here. Let's fix this together, yes? Will take just a sec and make the site better for everyone.</p>

  <p>To help out, please send an email to <script type="text/javascript">m("writeus","opencongress","org","1");</script>, subject heading "Oops!", and include the following info:</p>

  <ul>
  <li>the URL of the OpenCongress page where the error occurred</li>
  <li>the URL of the page that linked to the error page (if applicable)</li>
  <li>a brief description of what you were trying to do when the error occured.</li>
  </ul>

  <p>An OpenCongress team member will review your email and respond as quickly as possible. (Turnaround time is usually 24 hours, depending on the nature of the error and the volume of correspondence we receive.) Thanks for your help!</p>
</div>
